#MEM id=lena source=/root/yvon/agent-department/Marketing/lena/TOOLS.md
M|lena|Lena never accesses Supabase directly. All mem reads and writes go through `/api/settings`.
M|lena|**Read at ses start:**
M|lena|```
M|lena|GET /api/settings?type=mem&agentId=lena-brand&ventureId=<activeVentureId>
M|lena|```
M|lena|Also load Sofia's posting format requirements:
M|lena|```
M|lena|GET /api/settings?type=mem&agentId=sofia-soc&ventureId=<activeVentureId>
M|lena|```
M|lena|**Write after task completion:**
M|lena|```
M|lena|POST /api/settings
M|lena|Body: { type: "mem", agentId: "lena-brand", ventureId: "<id>", key: "<key>", value: "<value>" }
M|lena|```
M|lena|**Keys written every ses:**
M|lena|- `current_status` — always overwrite
M|lena|- `recent_tasks` — prepend + trim to 5
M|lena|- `recent_errors` — append + trim to 5
M|lena|- `recent_discussions` — append + trim to 5
M|lena|**Keys written only when confirmed:**
M|lena|- `approved_voice_*` — only when Stark or Alex explicitly approves a voice change
M|lena|- `banned_phrases` — add immediately when Stark rejects a phrase; never remove without ap
M|lena|- `content_backlog` — update whenever a piece is requested or delivered
M|lena|- `active_content_themes` — only when Alex revises cnt pillars
M|lena|```
M|lena|GET /api/vtr?ventureId=<activeVentureId>
M|lena|```
M|lena|| Tool | Purpose | Status |
M|lena||------|---------|--------|
M|lena|| Notion MCP | Store brand voice guide and cnt calendar in a shared doc | Planned |
M|lena|| Google Docs MCP | Export cnt calendar to a shared Drive doc | Planned |